WeepingFaceofNatureInBlydeRiverCanyon-375x251.jpg)](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:WeepingFaceofNatureInBlydeRiverCanyon.JPG)

大自然的哭臉（The Weeping Face of Nature）位於布萊德峽谷。圖片來源：Ptosio在維基百科(CC-BY-3.0)

